For anyone that's still having trouble, I figured out how to make this work.

1) Extract any of the .rar files ("extract here" is the easiest).
2) Mount the .cue file to a drive using Magic ISO.
3) Installation should start automatically. Ignore anything about registration, it'll work fine!
